Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.77,1:22:32.70,中英,,0,0,0,,贯穿这整部电影的\Nthat things forwards and backwards
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.70,1:22:34.16,中英,,0,0,0,,前前后后的情节\Nhappen throughout the film.
